config ENABLE_DS18B20_SENSORS
    bool "Enable DS18B20 temperature sensors"
    default y
    help
        Enable support for DS18B20 OneWire temperature sensors.
        When disabled, DS18B20 sensor configurations in sensors.json
        will be ignored and the driver code will not be compiled.

config ENABLE_NTC_SENSORS
    bool "Enable NTC thermistor sensors"
    default y
    help
        Enable support for NTC thermistor temperature sensors on ADC channels.
        When disabled, NTC_10K sensor configurations in sensors.json
        will be ignored and the driver code will not be compiled.

config ENABLE_GPIO_INPUT_SENSORS
    bool "Enable GPIO input sensors"
    default y
    help
        Enable support for digital sensors connected to GPIO inputs
        (door switches, limit switches, etc.).
        When disabled, GPIO_INPUT sensor configurations in sensors.json
        will be ignored and the driver code will not be compiled.
